=== PHOENIX_CHAMBER ===
# id: 81
# title: The Phoenix Chamber
# chinese_title: 凤凰室
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

A circular chamber pulsates with orange and gold energy. At its center, a bird-shaped energy construct repeatedly forms, blazes brilliantly, and disperses into embers — only to reform moments later. The cycle of creation and destruction is mesmerizing and beautiful.

* [Touch the phoenix construct at its peak]
  ~ gain_radical("凤")
  "凤" (fèng) — phoenix, mythical bird
* [Gather the embers after each cycle]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "灰" (huī) — ash, ember
* [Disrupt the cycle to capture the energy]
  ~ damage(5)
  "断" (duàn) — to break, to sever
* [Watch the full cycle three times]
  ~ heal(15)
  "生" (shēng) — life, to be born, to grow
